        dualConcepts - Type of interpretation for concepts outside the signature
        dualRoles - Type of interpretation for properties outside the signature
        considerImportsClosure - Treats the imported ontologies as well
        considerEntityAnnotations - Annotations are always local, but it could be interesting to maintain them in modules
        ignoreAssertions - The module will only extract the corresponding part from the TBOX
